Be prepared to be impressed with an awesome wide open split floor plan, huge kitchen with 42 inch espresso cabinets, loads of granite counter space and high ceilings makes this home perfect for entertaining. Sleep well at night knowing that this 3 year NEW home comes in tact with sturdy block construction, newer roof, AC, whole home water filtration system, appliances and much, much more! If you're looking to move to a city slated for tons of future growth and industry then look no further. Newer hospitals, restaurants and well known businesses have already opened or broken ground to help spring Deltona into a prosperous future. This home is also perfectly located within minutes to 1-4, golfing, shopping and restaurants which makes this home a must see. A short 30 minute drive takes you to Orlando & World Famous Beaches. This home is priced to move quick and will not last, so please be sure to schedule your showing today!
